Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:33.69,CN,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:36.98,CN,Satsuki,0,0,0,,为什么她也叫你「爸爸」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:39.99,CN,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,啊 啊 这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:49.37,CN,Shizuka's Dad,0,0,0,,我也不是很懂
