Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.10,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,静香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:15.48,CN,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那么 我们要把恰噼「取出来」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:16.31,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,静香
