Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:20.99,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,静香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:30.83,CN,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章鱼噼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:36.04,CN,Shizuka,0,0,0,,给我能调查被捉住人类的胃的道具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:39.04,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,我 我不知道啊噼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.80,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,这种道具没有噼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.72,CN,Shizuka,0,0,0,,诶 你说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:44.59,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,静香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:47.18,CN,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那算了 我自己想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.59,CN - singleup,Takopi,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.97,CN - singleup,Takopi,0,0,0,,静香 别这样噼
