Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:55.52,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,静香 你听我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.27,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,静香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.82,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,我们回去吧
