Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:37.78,CN,Marina,0,0,0,,章鱼噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.32,CN,Marina,0,0,0,,什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.41,CN,Happian A,0,0,0,,帮我摘下快乐果实噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:50.50,CN,Happian B,0,0,0,,来噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:52.50,CN,Happian A,0,0,0,,谢谢你噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.13,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,所以妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:20:00.88,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,用这个大快乐时钟 回到小学四年级
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.43,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,把久世静香杀了噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:11.10,CN,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:12.85,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:16.39,CN,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,若这是你的答案的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:17.90,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:21.61,CN,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,我会消除你的全部记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:24.87,CN,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,让你回到刚出生时的快乐状态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.79,CN,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,你一个人 来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:33.33,CN,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,破坏了快乐星球最为重要的「规则」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:36.96,CN,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,不被允许再次返回这颗行星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:41.80,CN,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,正因如此 你需要「重生」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:46.01,CN,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,忘记一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:49.77,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,这 这
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:53.23,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,这样子不行噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.06,CN,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:55.10,CN,Happians,0,0,0,,欸 什么噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:55.52,CN - singleup,Happians,0,0,0,,好恐怖噼
