Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:21:00.07,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,妈妈真是不讲理噼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:02.70,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.45,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,要去噼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:08.95,CN,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,但是你的记忆已经
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:12.50,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:20.84,CN,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,汪爱凯夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:26.64,CN,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,杀了是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:30.81,CN,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,为什么要这么用力触碰我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:34.85,CN,Happy Mama,0,0,0,,好好和我说话告诉我噼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.40,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,没事的噼 麻**酱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:44.95,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,我一定会让你快乐的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:48.16,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,就算失去记忆 我也一定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:54.07,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,**奈酱 **奈酱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:56.46,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:22:02.13,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,我到底 要让谁绽放笑容呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:12.22,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,为什么我会忘记呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:15.59,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,要杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:20.69,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,要杀了久世静香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:24.57,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,要杀了久世静香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:27.32,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,要把她毁灭到魂飞魄散
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:29.41,CN,Takopi,0,0,0,,我全都想起来了
